Package net.amoebaman.utils.nms

Interface Summary
NbtFactory.Wrapper Represents an object that provides a view of a native NMS class.
 

Class Summary
Attributes A class to ease the task of manipulating and editing the attributes system attached to the NBT data of item stacks.
Attributes.Attribute Stores all the information found within an attribute, and conveniently extracts and writes to NBT maps.
AttributeStorage A class that eases the manipulation of item attributes to attach persistent data to items, for plugin use.
NbtFactory Class for safely handling NBT compounds and tags.
ReflectionUtil Contains static methods useful for utilizing reflection as a workaround and alternative for directly importing NMS (net.minecraft.server) and OBC (org.bukkit.craftbukkit) classes, as plugins importing those classes will break with each update of Bukkit/CraftBukkit.
StatusBar Assorted methods for manipulating packets to spawn fake Ender Dragons and show players a status bar at the top of the screen using their health bar.
 

Enum Summary
Attributes.AttributeType Represents all of Minecraft's native attributes that are applicable to all living entities.
Attributes.Operation Represents the types of operations that Minecraft uses to determine the way the values of attributes are applied.
NbtFactory.StreamOptions Whether or not to enable stream compression.
ParticleEffect Contains an enumeration of all available particle effects, and methods for sending them to players via packets.
